ONS OF BOND</h2><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">WE, THE UNDERSIGNED, HEREBY AGREE TO THE FOLLOWING TERMS AND CONDITIONS SET FORTH IN THE FOLLOWING AGREEMENT WITH <u>Bond, James Bond, Inc.</u> WE UNDERSTAND THAT FAILURE TO COMPLY WITH THE FOLLOWING CONDITIONS MAY RESULT IN <b>BOND RECOVATON, LEGAL ACTION, FOREITURE OF COLLATERAL, OR ALL OF THE ABOVE.</b></p><h2 style="padding-top: 2pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">DEFENDANT                        CONDITIONS                     COS # 1     COS#2</h2><p style="padding-top: 1pt;padding-left: 75pt;text-indent: -67pt;line-height: 114%;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 1. Bond, James Bond, Inc. must be notified of any changes in: Address, Telephone Number, <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Employment, Other Arrest or any information given previously.</p><p style="padding-left: 77pt;text-indent: -69pt;line-height: 114%;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 2. Copies of final dispositions must be mailed/faxed to Bond, James Bond, Inc. to release <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Defendant &amp; Co-signers from bond and to return any collateral/security within 30 days.</p><p style="padding-left: 77pt;text-indent: -69pt;line-height: 114%;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 3. The Defendant is not allowed to leave the state without written consent of Bond, James <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Bond, Inc.</p><p style="padding-left: 77pt;text-indent: -69pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 4. The Defendant may be required to report/call in periodically as deemed necessary by <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Bond, James Bond, Inc. until the defendant’s case is resolved.</p><p style="padding-left: 75pt;text-indent: -67pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 5. If Defendant has to be returned to the jurisdiction of the courts, either from the <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Defendant is failure to appear in court or breach of conditions, the Defendant &amp; Co-</p><p style="padding-bottom: 2pt;padding-left: 75pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: left;">Signer(s) will be liable for all expenses incurred or monies owed to Bond, James Bond, Inc. the balance going forward shall be charged 18% interest.</p><table style="border-collapse:collapse;margin-left:5.4048pt" cellspacing="0"><tr style="height:14pt"><td style="width:459pt"><p class="s8" style="padding-left: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 11pt;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 6. Any disputes arising from terms &amp; conditions shall be heard by a court either in the</p></td><td style="width:67pt"><p class="s9" style="padding-right: 4pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 11pt;text-align: center;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></td><td style="width:58pt"><p class="s9" style="padding-right: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 11pt;text-align: right;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr style="height:16pt"><td style="width:459pt"><p class="s8" style="padding-right: 17pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 13pt;text-align: center;">County/State in which the Co-signers resides or Bartow County, GA.</p></td><td style="width:67pt"><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p></td><td style="width:58pt"><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p></td></tr><tr style="height:16pt"><td style="width:459pt"><p class="s8" style="padding-left: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 7. If the Defendant fails to appear in court, an in-house tracking fee of $250 in addition</p></td><td style="width:67pt"><p class="s9" style="padding-right: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: center;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></td><td style="width:58pt"><p class="s9" style="padding-right: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: right;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr style="height:16pt"><td style="width:459pt"><p class="s8" style="padding-left: 69pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">to any other expenses will be added to the Defendants account at an interest rate of</p></td><td style="width:67pt"><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p></td><td style="width:58pt"><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p></td></tr><tr style="height:16pt"><td style="width:459pt"><p class="s8" style="padding-left: 69pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 13pt;text-align: left;">18%.</p></td><td style="width:67pt"><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p></td><td style="width:58pt"><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p></td></tr><tr style="height:14pt"><td style="width:459pt"><p class="s8" style="padding-left: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 12pt;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 8. Waiver of extradition from all fifty states and/or territories of the United States.</p></td><td style="width:67pt"><p class="s9" style="padding-right: 5pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 12pt;text-align: center;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></td><td style="width:58pt"><p class="s9" style="padding-right: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 12pt;text-align: right;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></td></tr></table><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><span/></p><p style="padding-top: 2pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 9. Reasonable Attorney fees can be assessed-pursuant to O.C.G.A. 13-1-11.</p><p style="padding-top: 2pt;padding-left: 75pt;text-indent: -67pt;line-height: 113%;text-align: left;"><u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> 10. I have read and understand the terms and conditions of the bond contract between <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> the Defendant &amp; Co-signer(s) and <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc.</b></p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><h2 style="padding-left: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: center;">TERMS</h2><p style="padding-top: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: justify;">Bond Amount $<u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Bond Fee $<u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Other $<u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Amount Paid $<u> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> Type <span class="s10">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ca &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span class="s11"> </span>Collateral/Security (Explain) <span class="s10">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; None &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span class="s11"> </span>I/We understand that I/We Owe $<span class="s10"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span class="s11"> </span>For a Bond Fee for the Defendant <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</u></p><p style="padding-top: 1pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 13pt;text-align: left;">To Bond, James Bond, Inc.</p><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">I/We Agree to Pay $<span class="s10"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span class="s11"> </span>PER <span class="s10">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span class="s11"> </span>UNTIL Bond, James Bond Inc. IS PAID IN FULL. I/We Agree to make PAYMENTS OF $ <span class="s10">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>ON<span class="s10"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paid in full &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>.</p><p style="padding-top: 6pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><h2 style="padding-left: 2pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: center;">PROMISSORY NOTE/PROMISE TO PAY/PERMISSION</h2><p style="padding-top: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 91%;text-align: left;">I/We (THE UNDERSIGNED) agree to enter into this agreement for Bail Bonding with <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>for the amounts stated above on the request of the Defendant and Co-signer(s) (UNDERSIGNED) from the custody of the <span class="s2">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Cobb County &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span class="s4"> </span>jail.</p><ol id="l1"><li data-list-text="1."><p style="padding-top: 3pt;padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: -18pt;text-align: left;">I/We agree to reimburse <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>for all expenditures made or anticipated to be made to Courts, Attorney fees, Fugitive Recovery Agent, Etc. as a result of the Defendant’s failure to appear before the court at any place required by the court. This reimbursement shall occur not later than 10 days after <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>provides (or attempts to provide thru reasonable means) written notice to the undersigned of such expenditures.</p></li><li data-list-text="2."><p style="padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: -18pt;text-align: left;">I/We (UNDERSIGNED) agree if credit for the bail bond fee is extended to Defendant and Co-signer(s) that both parties are responsible and liable for payment of that fee to <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>regardless if Defendant is returned to the jurisdiction of the courts or settlement of case before or after their appointed court dates.</p></li><li data-list-text="3."><p style="padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: -17pt;line-height: 13pt;text-align: left;">This agreement is binding upon the successors and assigns of the undersigned.</p></li><li data-list-text="4."><p style="padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: -17pt;text-align: left;">As security for the prompt payment by the undersigned when due of all obligations arising from this agreement, the</p><p style="padding-top: 1pt;padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">undersigned hereby pledges, assigns, transfers ad grants to <b>Bond, James Bond, Ind. </b>A continuing security interest in lien upon the following described collateral: <b>any and all real and personal property, including but not limited to homes, vacant land, mobile homes, burial plots, bank accounts, certificates of deposit, money market accounts, stocks, bonds, negotiable instruments, cash, furnishings, appliances, jewelry, firearms, electronics, anything of value, etc.</b></p></li><li data-list-text="5."><p style="padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: -18pt;text-align: left;">I/We (Undersigned) agree to cooperate with <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>with respect to the perfection of the above- mentioned security interest and hereby appoints <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>and authorized representatives as the undersigned agent before the purpose of executing all documents and taking actions necessary to perfect and maintain the above-mentioned security interest.</p></li><li data-list-text="6."><p style="padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: -18pt;text-align: left;">The Undersigned hereby waives and releases all laws, now or hereafter in force, relating to exemption, appraisement, or stay of execution. The authority hereby granted to confess judgement shall not be exhausted by a single or partial exercise thereof but shall continue from time to time and at all times until the Undersigned has paid and satisfied all sums required to be paid under this agreement and until the Undersigned has preformed all other provisions hereof to be performed by the Undersigned.</p></li><li data-list-text="7."><p style="padding-left: 43pt;text-indent: -17pt;text-align: left;">Permission to use email and/or text as a means of communication regarding bail bond.</p></li></ol><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p class="s12" style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 1pt;text-align: left;"><span/>	<span/>	<span/></p><p style="padding-top: 3pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Co-Signer # 1                            Date            Defendant</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p class="s12" style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 1pt;text-align: left;"><span/>	<span/></p><p style="padding-top: 3pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Co-Signer # 2                                           Agent/Witness</p><p style="padding-top: 8pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 9pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 2pt;text-align: left;"><span/></p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><h2 style="padding-top: 2pt;padding-left: 239pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">RELEASE OF INFORMATION</h2><p style="padding-top: 6pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><span/></p><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">I, <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u>, <u>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </u> and</p><p style="padding-top: 11pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p class="s4" style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">None</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">, hereby authorize and direct my</p><p class="s6" style="padding-top: 3pt;padding-left: 37pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Defendant                Cosigner #1              Cosigner #2</p><p style="padding-top: 2pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 2pt;text-align: left;">Relatives, Employers, Bankers, The Federal Social Security Administration, The Internal Revenue Service, The State Department of Disability Insurance, The United States Armed Forces, The State Division of Motor Vehicles, The State, County and Municipal Boards of Education, and Credit reporting Agencies, all Municipal, County, State and Federal Law Enforcement Agencies, United States Postal Service, Medical Personnel and any other person or organizations having information concerning me or my whereabouts to give such information obtained to be used for the purpose of securing my appearance and/or apprehension for the purpose of securing reimbursement for any expenses incurred as a result of my non-appearance or failure to satisfy and financial agreements resulting from a bail bond performed at my request.</p><p style="padding-top: 3pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Further, I hereby waive my rights with respect to any privacy right and authorize the use of copies of this document by Investigators or Bounty Hunters and /or Authorized Representatives. I also give my permission for <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>or Authorized Representatives to obtain criminal history and/or photographs from Federal, State, County and Municipal Law Enforcement Agencies.</p><p style="padding-top: 3pt;padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">I hereby grant permission to <b>Bond, James Bond, Inc. </b>or Authorized Representatives to transport me across state lines and waive all rights or laws of extradition that might prevent me from returning to the jurisdiction of the court where I was released.</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p class="s12" style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 1pt;text-align: left;"><span/>	<span/>	<span/></p><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Co-Signer # 1                        Date                Defendant</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"><br/></p><p class="s12" style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 1pt;text-align: left;"><span/>	<span/></p><p class="s13" style="text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 8pt;text-align: left;">Rev: Nov. 2021</p><p style="text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;"/><p style="padding-left: 7pt;text-indent: 0pt;text-align: left;">Co-Signer #2                                           Agent/Witness</p></body></html>
